    <updated>2024-10-15T14:59:32-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>stonith404/pingvin-share</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;disallow passwort reset if it's a ldap user (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/2e692241c57b001c9312302523c6374c0c24ea0c"&gt;2e69224&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;error message for invalid max use count of reverse share (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/613bae90330a76c0964352a3fe927df3697309eb"&gt;613bae9&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;share can't be created if an invalid email is entered in mail recipients (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/d5cd3002a1661e58d584e12280be36f17948c38c"&gt;d5cd300&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;trim username, email and password on sign in and sign up page (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/77a092a3cf089a4aa8b9897b5ad14e5500181d10"&gt;77a092a&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;oauth:&lt;/strong&gt; add &lt;code&gt;post_logout_redirect_uri&lt;/code&gt; to OAuth logout redirect URI (#638) by @marvinruder &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/releases/tag/v1.2.1" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
